Program: Discovery
Title: Hope for an Aids vaccine
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwjv
Last Broadcast Date: 13 November 1995
Report on a promising new clue towards a vaccine and even a treatment for Aids. Also in the programme, looking for disease in ancient bones, examining the rings of Saturn and the German town Nordlingen and how it is built on tens of thousands of tonnes of diamonds. Presenter: Martin Redfern